http://www.conservative.org:80/wash_times/fields.8-11.html 204.71.237.88 19970209015004 text/html 5569
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 01:50:49 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 05-Aug-96 13:50:34 GMT
