<DOCNO>WT21-B14-147</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA074-000490-B010-36</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/townhall/columnists/howley/howl030896.html 204.71.237.88 19970209015723 text/html 6808
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
