<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/heritage/library/categories/education/bg1088.html 204.71.237.88 19970208225506 text/html 30251
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 22:55:47 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 10-Jan-97 19:32:19 GMT
